<p>A new column is added to the product.csv afterwards.</p>
</div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Note</strong>: If two properties have the same name, then the property with the lower ID will be overwritten. This way you can overwrite attributes which already exist by default (EAN, name etc.).</p>
